question:
####[ANCUR](https://twitter.com/anr_ruleswiki) [UFAQ 23](http://ancur.wikia.com/wiki/Whispers_in_Nalubaale_UFAQ) [Michael Boggs]
Can Remote Enforcement rez an Archer without forfeiting an agenda?
answer: No. If you install Archer with Remote Enforcement and do not forfeit an agenda, it will remain unrezzed.
